bdv.img.cache

Interface EmptyArrayCreator<A>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - access type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultEmptyArrayCreator

    public interface EmptyArrayCreator<A>
    Produce empty, invalid VolatileAccess to be used as placeholder invalid cell data.

    For common types, it should be created through the static helper method get(PrimitiveType, boolean) to get the desired primitive type and dirty / non-dirty variant.

    Author:
    Tobias Pietzsch
